# Pre-built binaries (icm.exe, icm-gui.exe) ARE committed on purpose so downloaders can run the
# host immediately via the launchers - do NOT ignore *.exe here.

# Runtime / dev cruft
icm-gui.error.log
*.pdb
_*

# refdocs/ is per-machine runtime: embedding vector caches (derived from corpus + embed model) and any
# locally-rebuilt corpora. All regenerated, so ignore it. The SHIPPED corpora + curated *.urls.txt
# source live in refdocs-seed/ (tracked) - the host reads those when refdocs/ has no local copy.
*/refdocs/

# Per-session memory (written by the chat; not source). Redirect output (e.g. an out/ dir) is
# user-chosen - add your own path here if you don't want generated files committed.
NOTES.md

# OS / editor
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
*.user
.vs/
